column1: Exported August 9 2021 2:04 PM. Reports are updated as and when Postman receives new notifications about message status.
'Read' status may not show up accurately for corporate and Singapore government recipients due to email filtering policies.

column3: Blacklisted: Your email will not be delivered to this recipient because Postman.gov.sg has determined that this recipient is not valid and might not exist.
Soft bounce: The email inbox might be full or the recipient might have an out-of-office message.
